{"id":123083,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2010/11/《自题小照：圣堂山上》/","date":"2010-11-17T20:22:38Z","modified":"2010-11-17T20:22:38Z","title":"《自题小照：圣堂山上》","content":"<p><p><span><br />\n《自题小照：圣堂山上》<span lang=\"EN-US\"></p>\n<p></span></span></p>\n<p><span>众山簇拥着圣堂山</span></p>\n<p><span>圣堂山在我脚下</span></p>\n<p><span>白云从脚下飘过</span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\"> </span></p>\n<p><span>白云的白与我领袖的白</span></p>\n<p><span>不一样的结构</span></p>\n<p><span>一样的性质</span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\"> </span></p>\n<p><span>人看见的是枭</span></p>\n<p><span>天看见的是木鸟</span></p>\n<p><span>让所有鹰熊望风而逃</span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\"> </span></p>\n<p><span>有古老的头颅</span></p>\n<p><span>为圣堂山作峰</span></p>\n<p><span>满山的桃李闹得更欢了</span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\"> </span></p>\n<p><span>最让我欣慰的是</span></p>\n<p><span>居然有人</span></p>\n<p><span>读懂了我的双眼</span></p>\n<p><span>让我紧闭的木门</span></p>\n<p><span>不能不中宵小开</span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\">2010-11-11</span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\"></p>\n<p></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\">2006.5.6摄于圣堂山<a href=\"http://blog.photo.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#url=http://static3.photo.sina.com.cn/orignal/500a591dg94c352f1df02\"><img src=\"http://static3.photo.sina.com.cn/middle/500a591dg94c352f1df02&#038;690\" /></a></p>\n<p></span></p>\n<div>\n<p><a href=\"http://move.blog.sina.com.cn/admin/blogmove/blogmove_msn.php\">MSN空间完美搬家到新浪博客!</a></p>\n</div>\n","author":176,"categories":[1],"tags":[]}